{"tid":1084483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"扮癡線嚇鳩樓上樓下啲精神病廢老有冇用？","createTime":"2019-03-30T12:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T21:28:05.000Z","uid":20241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9245c630cf085f9f9613c381da234835d0076c5d","tid":1084483,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"樓上樓下單位都有廢老住<br />\n日日都係屋企開餐 每次煮飯總係要啄啄啄 好撚嘈<br />\n去佢地單位扮死狗示好又過<br />\n道理又講過 屌又屌過<br />\n但都係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日突然諗到<br />\n扮癡線大叫邊撚個再啄就拎把刀落黎攬撚住一齊含家剷<br />\n其實啲廢老會唔會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cd4586fa5970c923fcba0b4b663af87fece83f","tid":1084483,"uid":1330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"會報警"},{"pid":"429f937d07f961b03e23a5a040e906135b393436","tid":1084483,"uid":67500,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"到時係你俾人拉入青山咋"},{"pid":"699b85f3a4d4f9982f657ce5838f11bb80b8ef67","tid":1084483,"uid":216521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d293fa84f9e29fea82fe5447ff3c9808d5ea96e9","tid":1084483,"uid":48964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"要見一次小一次，如果佢地有後生黎探佢地，一定要同後生投訴<br />\n<br />\n老一兩輩根本冇咩同理心/公德心"},{"pid":"988949d610555d6a397bdfde822010764cc05653","tid":1084483,"uid":236011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"話唔定到時會俾啲廢老兇尻翻你轉頭添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa65da74b7607010f28f2fc53232dc855de582c8","tid":1084483,"uid":62935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"988949d610555d6a397bdfde822010764cc05653","tid":1084483,"uid":236011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:42:54.000Z","m